function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)
	Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(idNPC, S_ANIM_WOUNDED)
	idLoc = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(S_MARKERLOC, idActor, false, 0, 0)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idNPC, idLoc, "NPC_Crawl", false)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(S_CONV_HELP, idNPC)
end

function Start()
	Hydra.QActorStopAllQueuedActions(idNPC)
	-- assign Crawl Death animset to override death pose and idle anim
	--Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idNPC, S_ANIMSET_CRAWL_DEATH)
	-- assign new idle after death anim completes
	Hydra.QActorAnimAndNewIdle(idNPC, S_ANIM_DIE, S_ANIM_DEAD)
end

-- Initial Setup
Hydra.ActorSetNoDamage(idNPC, false)
Hydra.ActorDamageByPercent(idNPC, 99.9)
Hydra.ActorSetNoDamage(idNPC, true)

Hydra.ActorSetBloody(idNPC, 0.75)
